title: BUCCHIGIRI?!
subTitle: After returning to his hometown, a youngster meets his childhood confidante and then, gets into a brawl with gangs until a genie enters his life.

title: Sound of Metal
subTitle: Ruben, a drummer, is distraught when he begins losing his hearing. However, things take a turn when he meets Joe, who heads a community comprising of people with hearing impairment.

title: Lake Placid vs. Anaconda
subTitle: A genetically modified anaconda and a giant crocodile escape captivity and enter a nearby lake. When the two massive creatures fight, the sheriff tries to prevent the town from being destroyed.

title: Chappie
subTitle: Chappie, a police robot, is stolen by criminals who treat it like their own child. With new programming, it becomes the first robot with the ability to feel and think for itself.

title: Bad Boys II
subTitle: Mike and Marcus, the Miami Police Department detectives, investigate the flow of drugs into Miami. Their search leads them to a dangerous drug lord who is planning to control the city's drug trade.

title: Bloodshot
subTitle: A soldier who died on duty is resurrected and given superhuman abilities by the RST Corp. But soon he realises the truth about his past and his resurrection and sets out to get revenge.

title: Afraid
subTitle: Curtis and his family are asked to install an artificial intelligence program in their house in a bid to test it. However, they soon begin to experience disturbing occurrences.

title: The Adventures of Tintin
subTitle: Tintin's new model ship sparks an adventure of intrigue and theft. He uncovers a historical mystery involving treasure, rival groups and a quest for scrolls revealing a sunken ship's location.

title: Ghost Rider
subTitle: Motorcycle stuntman Johnny Blaze gives up his soul to save his father and becomes the Ghost Rider to fight against Blackheart, the son of Mephistopheles, the devil himself.

title: Terminator Salvation
subTitle: Judgement Day has occurred and skynet has all but exterminated modern society. Now John Connor leads the resistance against skynet but is unsure of victory until he encounters Marcus Wright.

title: Bullet Train
subTitle: Ladybug, a professional assassin, is assigned to retrieve a briefcase from a bullet train. Soon, he finds himself battling many other killers who board the same train but with a different objective.

title: The Walk
subTitle: Philippe Petit, a French street performer, dreams of performing daring stunts. He attempts to walk between the Twin Towers of the World Trade Center in New York on a tightrope.

title: Zombieland: Double Tap
subTitle: Columbus, Tallahassee, Wichita and Little Rock set out on a mission to protect the rest of humanity by fighting evolved zombies while also battling their own internal demons.

title: The Water Horse
subTitle: Young Angus Mac Morrow discovers a mysterious egg that grows up to be the Loch Ness monster. As they form a strong relationship, the boy's family refuses to believe in the creature's existence.

title: Metallic Rouge
subTitle: An android named Nean Rouge with a human investigator Naomi Orthmann pursue rebel dissidents to Mars in a thrilling chase.

title: BUCCHIGIRI?!
subTitle: Araji reunites with old friend Mataka, but their reunion sparks power struggles and conflict.

title: You Don't Mess With the Zohan
subTitle: Zohan, an Israeli anti-terrorist commando, stages his own death when he gets tired of his job and goes to New York City to follow his dream of being a hairstylist.

title: Insidious: Chapter 2
subTitle: Josh Lambert and his family relocate to his mother's old house in the hopes of recovering from past trauma. However, they soon encounter strange and chilling paranormal events.

title: Charlie's Angels
subTitle: Charlie, a wealthy mystery figure, tasks three capable and captivating women with the job of finding Eric Knox, a genius in software development and the leader of Knox Enterprises.

title: Miss Bala
subTitle: Gloria gets abducted by a group of criminals when she visits Mexico to meet her friend Suzu. Later, she uses her wit to survive in the cruel world of crime.

title: Daddio
subTitle: A woman takes a cab ride back home from the airport. En route, she unexpectedly has an insightful conversation with the driver regarding the important relationships in life.

title: Harold and the Purple Crayon
subTitle: Harold's drawings spring to life when he ventures into the real world. His purple crayon accidentally creates challenges and he and his friends must safeguard both worlds.

title: Escape Room: Tournament of Champions
subTitle: Ben and Zoey find themselves trapped in a series of deadly escape rooms with four others. They try to survive and find a way out as they slowly discover that they have played the game before.

title: Hotel Transylvania
subTitle: Count Dracula runs a high-end resort for monsters and is overprotective of his daughter, Mavis. When Johnny, a human, enters the hotel, Count Dracula tries to prevent Mavis from falling for him.

title: Welcome to the Jungle
subTitle: A group of co-workers embark on a team-building exercise on an uninhabited island. However, when their ex-marine guide is killed, they are left stranded and must struggle to survive.
A spaceship crash lands on prehistoric Earth, leaving only two survivors. Soon, they must survive against the hostile terrain and vicious creatures.

title: Venom: The Last Dance
subTitle: As Eddie and Venom are tirelessly pursued by forces from both of their worlds, they find themselves out of options and left with a shattering last resort.

title: The Social Network
subTitle: In 2003, Harvard University sophomore, Mark Zuckerberg, creates the social networking platform called Facebook. But along with the popularity of the site he also gets dragged into two lawsuits.

title: Brightburn
subTitle: Tori and Kyle find a baby boy in a spaceship and adopt him as their own child, Brandon. However, after turning 12, Brandon learns that he has superpowers and begins to use them for sinister purposes.

title: Spider-Man: Far From Home
subTitle: Peter Parker, the beloved superhero Spider-Man, faces four destructive elemental monsters while on holiday in Europe. Soon, he receives help from Mysterio, a fellow hero with mysterious origins.

title: Metallic Rouge
subTitle: Android Rouge and partner Naomi are on a mission to Mars to eliminate the Immortal Nine, artificial humans threatening the government.

title: Anacondas: Trail of Blood
subTitle: When an experiment goes wrong, a genetically enhanced anaconda offspring is unleashed. Possessing the power to regenerate, it quickly creates panic and destruction.

title: Alpha
subTitle: Keda, the young son of a tribe chief, is accidentally left behind, and must survive in the wilderness. He encounters an injured wolf abandoned by its pack, and the two form a bond.

title: Captain Phillips
subTitle: Somali pirates attack the Maersk Alabama, a container ship, while it is on its course to Kenya. Richard Phillips, the captain of the ship, uses his wits to negotiate with them to save his crew.

title: The Angry Birds Movie
subTitle: Red, Chuck and Bomb have always been the outcasts within a community of flightless birds on an island. But when mysterious green pigs intrude the island, it is up to them to figure out the reason.

title: Hellboy
subTitle: Hellboy is a demonic warrior who protects the Earth from paranormal threats. When an enemy from his past makes a comeback, it is up to him and his team to stop the villain once and for all.

title: White House Down
subTitle: When terrorists suddenly invade the White House, police officer John Cale springs into action to protect his daughter and the President of the United States.

title: Dumb Money
subTitle: Keith Gill, a humble financial analyst known only as 'Roaring Kitty' on social media, sparks a revolution against Wall Street through the mass buying of stock in a failing video game retailer.

title: Men in Black: International
subTitle: Agent M, a probationary member of the MIB, teams up with Agent H and uncovers a sinister plot that reveals a traitor in the organisation aiding an alien invasion.

title: Kill 'Em All 2
subTitle: Partnered by the CIA, Phillip and Vanessa are back home to Europe. But a vengeful Russian-French terrorist Vlad, is here after Philip to settle scores for his dead brother. Carnage follows.
